OL,3,CMy Community Series: The bowls club
OL,4,Cgetting islanders on their feet
OL,6,FIt's a sport you can take at your own
OL,7,Fpace, but done by the pros, it's full
OL,8,Fof poise and precision.
OL,10,FSt Saviour's Bowls Club in Jersey sees
OL,11,Fislanders come for much more than just
OL,12,Fsport, although its members take that
OL,13,Fseriously too.
OL,15,FSally Black is a member who competed
OL,16,Fat last year's Island Games in
OL,17,FGuernsey.
OL,19,FShe told ITV News: "I got a bronze
OL,20,Fmedal which I'm very proud of. I hold
OL,21,Fmy heart to the club."
