OL,3,CMy Community Series: The bowls club
OL,4,Cgetting islanders on their feet
OL,6,FAnother avid member, Paul Du Feu,
OL,7,Fpraises the impact the club has
OL,8,Flocally.
OL,10,FPaul said: "It really sort of hit me
OL,11,Fbecause I think we are a community.
OL,13,F"We are a group of people who've come
OL,14,Ftogether, many of us quite later on in
OL,15,Flife, from very different backgrounds,
OL,16,Fand I just feel you're going to a very
OL,17,Fhappy place where you can feel safe
OL,18,Fand relaxed and just be yourself.
