OL,3,CMy Community Series: The bowls club
OL,4,Cgetting islanders on their feet
OL,6,FHenry Picot is another member
OL,7,Fencouraging more people to come and
OL,8,Fgive bowls a go.
OL,10,FHe said: "They could easily do it. I
OL,11,Fthink it'd be better for them to try
OL,12,Fand get out in the fresh air with
OL,13,Fcompany and get the exercise instead
OL,14,Fof just sitting at home and watching
OL,15,Ftelevision."
OL,17,FThe club says it is hoping to recruit
OL,18,Fsome younger members too.
OL,20,FSo why not give it a go? You might
OL,21,Fjust be bowled over.
