OL,6,FMembers of St Saviour's Bowls Club
OL,7,Fwere interviewed as part of ITV
OL,8,FChannel's 'My Community Series' which
OL,9,Fcelebrates the importance of coming
OL,10,Ftogether - it can be a cookery class,
OL,11,Fa sports session, friends meeting up
OL,12,Fand much more.
OL,14,FTo share what community means to you,
OL,15,Fsend an email with the subject 'My
OL,16,FCommunity' to channelnews@itv.com with
OL,17,Fa few details about what you do and
OL,18,Fwhy it is so special so we can come
OL,19,Falong and hear all about it.
